textBeforeTable: How to link The following is excerpted directly from MediaWiki Help:Linking, since I often forget how to do this... See this for Basic Formatting. See this for help on images See this for help on tables like the one below. See this for advanced formatting Links to MediaWiki Helpful Topics Seeing that this is such a short page, go look at some pictures of cute puppies to pass the time a bit and then come back. See this page if you wish to format your page to look nicer or have more features: MediaWiki Help: Editing Pages Thanks. There's not much to help with, all you do is type what you're looking for in the search box on the left, and go. So, maybe you can help me. If you see any typos or some information that's clearly incorrect, please feel free to request and account and edit it. If you really need help doing something contact me, and I'll see what I can do. search navigation, Jump to: From CLUMP Help:Contents
